b'@carIyfever We have learned to not expect a thing- but that is what is so exciting.  I think I\xe2\x80\x99ll keep writing for you tho. Thanks for being such nice ears about it all.'
b'@boywithagetaway Leonard Cohen is very sexy and very good.'
b'@doublemantra13 I write always but I\xe2\x80\x99m picky cause your pretty ears only deserve the best but I promise once I figure out this disco it\xe2\x80\x99s all for you.'

b'@benjiii__al I can remember that every night before the Prince would lift me (aka Joe)- I\xe2\x80\x99d whisper in his ear what I had for lunch. A 20 pound dress and a burger dear. He\xe2\x80\x99d always die laughing and that was my favourite part.'
b'@ankIebracelet Dedicated side B was very fun for the fact that it was experimental'

b'@podcastdoors My friend Jamie used to come to the small club gigs and would always say \xe2\x80\x9cit\xe2\x80\x99s great when you can hear the ice clink\xe2\x80\x9d and that was reference to when the room got quiet and listened. I think nothing beats that.'
b'@happythinkingg I like to make Italian dishes best. Learning as I go but home made pasta is a thing I take great pride in.'
b'@perryfenty LA hallucinations was a last min decision. I had friends from Canada who knew me well and were excited for this song to be heard. I get it.'
b'@sondheim2011 I miss waking up and opening the curtain to the back bus window and not knowing what I was going to see. There was something really cool about that feeling.'
